snippet.title: Pygmy Longplay (Atari 2600 Game)
snippet.description:
- Pygmy Longplay (Atari 2600 Game) -

Aside from the name change and the color shift of your character from red to green, Lock 'n' Chase remains essentially unchanged. —it even maintains the same absurd level of difficulty, lol.

#retrogamingloft #pygmylongplay #pygmyatari2600
